-* When the Sheriff John Brown
come for you? *
-Stop! Now! Stop!

00:18.933 --> 00:20.700
-(clattering)
-Heads up!

00:20.733 --> 00:23.500
-* Bad boys, bad boys,
whatcha gonna do... *

00:23.533 --> 00:25.933
I smoked some marijuana!
I'm a marijuana smoker!

00:25.967 --> 00:27.800
-* Bad boys, bad boys *
-Crawl out!

00:27.833 --> 00:29.200
* Whatcha gonna do... *

00:29.233 --> 00:30.433
-Hands up! Hands up!

00:30.467 --> 00:32.333
Hold it! Hold it!
Hold it! Hold it!

